> ; The hero starts the adventure with some clothing of his own. During the game
> ; we need to keep track of clothing items belonging to the hero vs items of the
> ; store for various reasons (eg. when we'll script store clerks to carry the
> ; hero clothing while he tries on store items, and to pick up and put back store
> ; items dropped by the hero).
